# Web App Family Rules

- Apply this rule when `projectFamily` is `web-app`.
- Use `docs/ai/project-bootstrap.md`, `docs/ai/project-family-map.md`, and `docs/ai/stack-matrix.md` before structural stack changes.
- Treat `TypeScript + React + Vite` as the default baseline unless a documented exception exists.
- Keep route, menu, env, API binding, and screen-level smoke validation aligned.
- Combine this rule with the `frontend` runtime-role rule.
